'''Joseph Reiser''' was a longtime general manager of the [[Omega SA|Omega]] watch company. He has been credited as the architect of the worldwide brand notoriety.

==Biography==
Joseph Reiser was already the President of the [[Société Suisse pour l'Industrie Horlogère|SSIH]] Group, when 1958 he had to take over the management of [[Omega SA]], upon Paul Emile Brand's death.

Under his guidance, Omega established subsidiaries in its main markets, and extended its distribution and customer services worldwide.

